title: The Eternal Supreme
description: Read Full Raw The Eternal Supreme English At Manhua Website One of the Conferred Martial Emperors, Gu Feiyang, passed away in the Tiandang Mountains and was reincarnated 15 years later as Li Yunxiao of the State of Tianshui, embarking on a heaven-defying journey against the innumerable geniuses of the time. The nine levels of the Martial Art; the Divine Realms of the ten quarters. From then on, the whole world fell into chaos! Eternal Supreme, Everlasting Supreme, 万古至尊 (II) The Ultimate of All Ages The Ancient Sovereign of Eternity
